CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

April 29, 2014

[Cite as 04/29/2014 Case Announcements #2, 2014-Ohio-1815.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2009-1292. State ex rel. Doner v. Zehringer.

In Mandamus. This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing of respondents’ cross-motion for leave to file supplemental evidence. It is ordered by the court that the motion is granted.

O’Connor, C.J., and French, J., dissent.
